title: [Bug Fix] - `/vertex_ai/` was not detected as llm_api_route on pass through but `vertex-ai` was

body:
## [Bug Fix] - `/vertex_ai/` was not detected as llm_api_route on pass through but `vertex-ai` was

Docs told me to use `/vertex_ai/` and that did not work: https://docs.litellm.ai/docs/pass_through/vertex_ai

This PR fixes the issue, allowing /vertex_ai/ and /vertex-ai/ as llm api routes
